Need for Speed: The Run runs across America.
Reviews
Originally, carefree driving turns into a routine morning road to the neck because of a series of completely unnecessary laidations.
The ambition has largely been fulfilled, but nothing is valid when no one apparently wanted to do anything extra.
A new part with the subtitle The Run woke up before the release of high expectations.
